  "description": [
    "Page 4 Jewish Doctors Find Many Cures BY DAVID SCHWARTZ Dr Ernest Boris Chain a Jewish biologist who was forced to flee Germany after the advent of the Nazis was cowinner of the 1945 Nobel prize for physiology and medicine for his work in de veloping penicillin We mention this fact because we think it ought to be interesting to the deans of our medical schools Nowhere in American life has the Nazi idea of race discrimination made head way as in our medical colleges which strictly limit the number of Jewish students Once again the old theme that antiSemitism is as harmful to the nonJew as to the Jew is proven Will the medical colleges dare bar from their colleges the discoveries of Jews as they now do Jews themselves Will they fail to teach the values of penicillin Will they dare eliminate from their studies all that the Jew Paul Ehrlich taught them Almost all modern medicines hopes for the future rest upon Ehrlich It was he who showed that the inside of the body might be made to talk It was Ehrlichs discovery of the value of dye stuffs to obtain reactions within the body that made"
